Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}能做的事情也只有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}なにもできないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}在黑暗中盲目張望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:49.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}またひとつ　消えていった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:49.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}還剩下一個即將消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:54.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}音も立てずに 今そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:54.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}現在悄悄地 沒有聲音的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:59.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}あなたの夢のかけらが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:59.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}你的夢想的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:04.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}Be Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:04.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}Be Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:09.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}もう 沈黙のままで  涙を隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:09.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}即使只能保持沉默 也不要隱藏眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:14.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}繰り返されてく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:14.68,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}循環往復
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}絶望の先に
